  * New upstream release 
    Dropped patches, applied upstream:
     + Fix-GHCi-segfault-on-linux-powerpc
     + hurd-is-ELF
     + use-llvm-3.0
     + memcpy-ffi
     + fix-PPC-right-shift-bug
     + no-useless-time
     + fix-ppc-ghci-segfault
